org.knime.core.node.config.base

Interface ConfigBaseRO

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Iterable<String>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ConfigRO, ModelContentRO, NodeSettingsRO
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Config, ConfigBase, ModelContent, NodeSettings

    public interface ConfigBaseRO
extends Iterable<String>
    Interface implements only read access functions for ConfigBase objects providing methods for base data types only..
    Author:
    Thomas Gabriel, University of Konstanz

      • getPassword

        String getPassword(String key,
                   String encryptionKey)
            throws InvalidSettingsException
        Returns a decrypted password. If no password is stored under the key an exception is thrown.
        Parameters:
        key - the key, must not be null
        encryptionKey - key used for encrypting the password
        Returns:
        a decrypted password, may be null
        Throws:
        InvalidSettingsException - if no password for the given key exists

      • getPassword

        String getPassword(String key,
                   String encryptionKey,
                   String def)
        Returns a decrypted password. If no password is stored under the key the given default is returned instead. The default value is not decrypted, it's returned as provided.
        Parameters:
        key - the key, must not be null
        encryptionKey - key used for encrypting the password
        def - the (decrypted) default value
        Returns:
        a decrypted password, may be null

      • getTransientString

        String getTransientString(String key)
        Returns a transient string if present or null if no longer available (setting restored from disc).
        Parameters:
        key - the key, must not be null
        Returns:
        that string or null.
        Since:
        5.3
